Featuring an open-concept floorplan with a private primary suite, two guest bedrooms, and an eat-in kitchen that overlooks a living room full of natural light. The kitchen features a spacious pantry, granite countertops, stainless appliances, a large island, and a view of the low-maintenance backyard with a covered patio and privacy fence.
